      "text": "Let this courage define you",
      "description": "You're braver than you knew.",
      "resultText": "The act of courage changes how you see yourself. If you could do that, what else might you be capable of? You start seeking out opportunities to be brave, to help, to stand up. The fear is still there, but now you know you can act through it. You're discovering an identity as someone who doesn't back down. It's empowering, though there's a part of you that wonders if you're starting to seek danger for its own sake.",
